Step 12
Step name: Create an Auto scaling group
Instructions:
1) Select the LT/LC or AMI that should be used to create your ASG
2) Select the TG to add your EC2 Instance of the app server
3) Select your scaling policy to determine how/when your ASG will scale your EC2 Instance
4) You can add an SNS Topic for your configuration to notify you of activities in your ASG
5) Create your Auto scaling group.
